# RQ-53-10-01-101: Lightning Zone 1A Protection (200 kA)

## Requirement Statement
The nose cone shall withstand direct lightning strike up to 200 kA peak current without structural damage or ignition of fuel system.

## Rationale
Nose cone is in Lightning Zone 1A (high probability of strike attachment).

## Acceptance Criteria
- Conductive diverter strips installed
- Bonding resistance < 2.5 milliohm
- No burn-through or delamination after 200 kA test
- No arcing to fuel system components

## Compliance Status
Design complete, test planned Q3 2026

## Traceability
- Parent: CS-25.581, AC 20-136A
